text: Phred may refer to: *Phred base calling, a program used in molecular biology *Phred quality score, a term used in molecular biology *Phred (Doonesbury), a character from the comic strip Doonesbury *Phred on Your Head Show, a children's television show *The URL with Phred Show, a spin-off of the above ==See also== *Fred (disambiguation)
